cdata.name: ILCoin Token
cdata.desc: ILCOIN is a cryptocurrency developed by R&G GmbH. It is mined using SHA-256 Proof-of-Work (POW) technology. ILCOINwants to evolve and become the foundation of a new, global digital currency-based economic system. Members of this system may earn, accumulate, spend and trade ILCoins for the benefit of themselves and the entire community.
